    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-400 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-7">
        Our mission is to bridge the gap between technology and people by building user-centric solutions that make lives easier, businesses more efficient, and the world more connected. We are committed to sustainability, innovation, and continuous improvement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-400 mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-7">
        We envision a future where technology empowers individuals and organizations to achieve their fullest potential. Our vision is to be at the forefront of innovation, shaping the digital landscape for generations to come.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-400 mb-4">What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Customer-first approach with a focus on user experience</li>
        <li>Innovative solutions powered by the latest technologies</li>
        <li>A diverse team with a global perspective</li>
        <li>Commitment to quality and continuous improvement</li>
        <li>Sustainable practices and ethical values</li>
